	  to vars_dvipdfm

2004-03-17 14:28  dan

	* testsuite/: bmake_ref/vars_latex2rtf.ref,
	  gmake_ref/vars_latex2rtf.ref, golden.mk: add vars_latex2rtf test

2004-03-17 13:07  dan

	* COPYING: update copyright date

2004-03-17 13:04  dan

	* latex-mk.in: add support for monitoring certain files such as the
	  .toc, .lof, and .lot files (table of contents, list of figures,
	  list of tables).  If these files change or appear after a latex
	  run, then an addition run will be triggered.	This addresses a
	  bug noted by Herve Quiroz and reproduced by myself where the
	  table of contents might not get properly updated.

2004-02-02 22:30  dan

	* example/README-example.txt: LATEX-MK -> LATEX_MK

