	  dependencies.

2002-10-17 06:54  dan

	* latex.mk.in.in, tgif.mk.in.in: many fixes for gmake.	Uses
	  gmake-3.80 features, but the other approach to the dynamic
	  dependencies and targets was a total hack which proved to not be
	  portable across different versions of gmake.	The big change here
	  is how we handle multiple top level documents with gmake.

