	* configure.ac, latex.mk.in.in, tgif.mk.in.in, doc/latex-mk.texi,
	  example/Makefile.am, example/makefile.in: many changes to allow
	  GNU make to deal with multiple documents per directory and some
	  common and some shared dependencies.	Now fully supports things
	  like:

